---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="About me" id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="h-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    I'm an <span class="text-primary">honors cybersecurity student</span> at the <span class="text-secondary">University of Akron</span>, focusing on <span class="text-primary">Computer Information Systems</span> with a specialization in cybersecurity. Passionate about penetration testing and cybersecurity trends, I'm currently an <span class="text-secondary">IT security intern at The Hershey Company</span>.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="https://github.com/Coontzy1"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-6 py-4 border-2 border-current"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="telescope" class="h-8" />
      <span>Check out my GitHub</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/austin-coontz/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-6 py-4 border-2 border-current"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="rocket" class="h-8" />
      <span>Follow me on LinkedIn</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
